Interface EjbRelationType

public interface EjbRelationType

A representation of the model object 'Ejb Relation Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Ejb Relation Name
  • Ejb Relationship Role
  • Ejb Relationship Role1
  • Id
